\begin_layout Standard
Note that the Power Levels
\begin_inset Index idx
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Power Level
\end_layout

\end_inset

 follow an easy to remember pattern up to 12.
 At even levels you use two dice of the same size, and that size matches
