 8 is d8, d8...).
 Odd levels have one die of the next higher level and one of the next lower
 (Power Level 5 is a d6 and a d4, Power Level 7 is a d8 and a d6, Power
 Level 9 is a d10 and a d8...).
 It gets a tiny bit trickier once you get past d12: past d12 the dice go
 d8+5, d10+5, d12+5, d8+10, d10+10, and so on.
 However, since at any given Scope the Powers and Shticks begin at around
 PL 4-6, it will be quite a while before that becomes an issue.
